/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. /ITMaÚariv/XX is the heart of the Festival evening service. As on
weekdays, it contains several parts: the Shema and its blessings, the /ITAmidah/XX
(silent prayer), and the /ITAleynu/XX. On Shabbat there are several additions:
/ITVeshameru/XX (Exodus 31:16-17), a brief reprise of the /ITAmidah/XX, and
Kiddush.    /SC/XXD.A.T./XX/PR
